aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
;Uses uses SystemModDef ; Rule ; Classification Type tWF_Generated_JobClassification_318776651_8:(MonthlySalaried, BiweeklySalaried, HourlySalaried) func Contract__Classifications__JobClassification:tWF_Generated_JobClassification_318776651_8 if self.EvaluateClassificationFromRank(1,1,'Contract__Classifications__JobClassification') _Result = tWF_Generated_JobClassification_318776651_8(self.V_ForClassificationEvaluation) endIf endFunc
; FieldDesc Type tWF_Generated_MinimumNumberofWorkinghours_318776651_10:(_20, _25, _30, _35, _40) func Contract__Dynamic_Data__MinimumWorkingHoursPerWeek:tWF_Generated_MinimumNumberofWorkinghours_318776651_10 type tpValue : .tWF_Generated_MinimumNumberofWorkinghours_318776651_10 var p : tWF_Generated_MinimumNumberofWorkinghours_318776651_10 if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(0,2,'Contract__Dynamic_Data__MinimumWorkingHoursPerWeek') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
; VarDesc
Proc WFCalculate(out Result :Boolean) Result = True ;If the Minimum number of working hours are less than the minimum defined by the Group if Contract__Dynamic_Data__MinimumWorkingHoursPerWeek = _20 if Member__WorkingHoursPerWeek < 20 Result = False endIf elseif Contract__Dynamic_Data__MinimumWorkingHoursPerWeek = _25 if Member__WorkingHoursPerWeek < 25 Result = False endIf elseif Contract__Dynamic_Data__MinimumWorkingHoursPerWeek = _30 if Member__WorkingHoursPerWeek < 30 Result = False endIf elseif Contract__Dynamic_Data__MinimumWorkingHoursPerWeek = _35 if Member__WorkingHoursPerWeek < 35 Result = False endIf else if Member__WorkingHoursPerWeek < 40 Result = False endIf endIf if Result = False AppendComment('The Member is not eligible for this coverage as the number of working hours are less than the minimum defined by the Group') endIf ;If the Member is hourly Salaried if Contract__Classifications__JobClassification = HourlySalaried Result = False AppendComment('The Member is not eligible as he is an hourly salaried employee') endIf
end

aWFRuleDesc.RuleDescription:
Waiting Period on Effective Date : Defined by Group Waiting Period After Effective Date : Defined by Group (First of Month After)
For Initial Enrollment, Coverage Effective Date = GBP Effective Date For Ongoing Enrollment, Coverage Effective Date = First of Month after Signature Date + Waiting Period after Effective Date)
Grace Period : 32 Days
aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
;Uses uses WFTypes ; Rule ; Classification ; FieldDesc func Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodonEffectiveDateInDays:Int4 type tpValue : .Int4 var p : Int4 if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(0,5,'Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodonEffectiveDateInDays') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
func Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodAfterEffectiveDateinDays:Int4 type tpValue : .Int4 var p : Int4 if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(1,5,'Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodAfterEffectiveDateinDays') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
; VarDesc
Proc WFCalculate(out Result :tWFDate) var Eligibility_End_Date_At_Issuance : tWFDate var Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance : tWFDate var Coverage_Effective_Date : tWFDate
;-------------Member Eligibility End Date At Issuance----------- Eligibility_End_Date_At_Issuance = Member__HireDate + Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodonEffectiveDateInDays ;-----------Initial Enrollment Coverage Effective Date Calculation if Coverage__Enrollment_Period__Current_Enrollment_Period = cInitialEnrollment if Eligibility_End_Date_At_Issuance > GBP__Effective_Date Coverage_Effective_Date = Eligibility_End_Date_At_Issuance elseif Eligibility_End_Date_At_Issuance <= GBP__Effective_Date Coverage_Effective_Date = GBP__Effective_Date endIf if Coverage_Effective_Date < Member__Division__EffectiveDate Coverage_Effective_Date = Member__Division__EffectiveDate elseif Coverage_Effective_Date < Contract__Signature_Date Coverage_Effective_Date = Contract__Signature_Date endIf endIf ;----------Member Eligibility End Date After Issuance---------- if Coverage__Enrollment_Period__Current_Enrollment_Period = cOngoingEnrollment Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance = Member__HireDate + Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodAfterEffectiveDateinDays ;First of Next Month After the Waiting Period is added if DateAsDay(Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance) <> 1 IncMonths(1, Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance) SetDay(1, Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance) endIf if Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance > Contract__Signature_Date Coverage_Effective_Date = Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance elseif Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance <= Contract__Signature_Date Coverage_Effective_Date = Contract__Signature_Date if Coverage_Effective_Date < Member__Division__EffectiveDate Coverage_Effective_Date = Member__Division__EffectiveDate endIf endIf endIf ; Result = Coverage_Effective_Date
end

aWFRuleDesc.RuleDescription: A member enrollment is considered a "late enrollment" if the following is true during the Ongoing Enrollment - Signature Date > Eligibility End Date + Grace Period - Eligibility End Date = Member Hire Date + Waiting Period
aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLI_LifeDisabilityRuleEngine) (Def Version:1) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFTypes, aWLIMemberContractRoot
function Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodAfterEffectiveDateinDays return Int4 type tpValue : .Int4
var p : Int4
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(0, 5, 'Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodAfterEffectiveDateinDays') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Boolean) var Eligibility_End_Date : tWFDate
Result = False ;------------Member Eligibility End Date Calculation--------------- Eligibility_End_Date = self.Member__HireDate + self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodAfterEffectiveDateinDays ;-----------Late Entrant Underwriting Rule------------- if self.Coverage__Enrollment_Period__Current_Enrollment_Period = cOngoingEnrollment if self.Contract__Signature_Date > Eligibility_End_Date + self.Coverage__Grace_Period_Nb_Days Result = True self.AppendComment('This Member enrollment is considered as late enrollment') endIf endIf endProc

aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLI_LifeDisabilityRuleEngine) (Def Version:2) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFTypes, WLIClaim
type tWF___EliminationPeriodforSTD56 : (A_0_I_7, A_7_I_7, A_0_I_14, A_14_I_14, A_30_I_30, A_90_I_90)
function Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD return tWF___EliminationPeriodforSTD56 type tpValue : .tWF___EliminationPeriodforSTD56
var p : tWF___EliminationPeriodforSTD56
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(0, 5, 'Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFDate) var incDays : Int4
incDays = 0 if self.TemporaryDisability__DisabilityKind = ckAccident if (self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD = A_0_I_7) or (self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD = A_0_I_14) incDays = 0 elseif self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD = A_7_I_7 incDays = 7 elseif self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD = A_14_I_14 incDays = 14 elseif self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD = A_30_I_30 incDays = 30 else incDays = 90 endIf elseif self.TemporaryDisability__DisabilityKind = ckIllness if (self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD = A_0_I_7) or (self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD = A_7_I_7) incDays = 7 elseif (self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD = A_0_I_14) or (self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD = A_14_I_14) incDays = 14 elseif self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__EliminationPeriodforSTD = A_30_I_30 incDays = 30 else incDays = 90 endIf endIf Result = self.Loss__EventDate Result += incDays endProc

if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(2, 5, 'Coverage__Dynamic_Data__AdditionalBenefitforLTD') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFNum8) var amount : tWFAmount
amount = 0 if self.Coverage__Classifications__LTDBenefitPlan = BaseBuyUp_AdditionalBenefit if self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__BaseBuyUpPercentageforLTD = _40Percent amount = (0.4 + self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__AdditionalBenefitforLTD) * self.Member__Annual_Earnings__Salary elseif self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__BaseBuyUpPercentageforLTD = _50Percent amount = (0.5 + self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__AdditionalBenefitforLTD) * self.Member__Annual_Earnings__Salary elseif self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__BaseBuyUpPercentageforLTD = _60Percent amount = (0.6 + self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__AdditionalBenefitforLTD) * self.Member__Annual_Earnings__Salary else amount = (2 / 3 + self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__AdditionalBenefitforLTD) * self.Member__Annual_Earnings__Salary endIf else if self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__BaseBuyUpPercentageforLTD = _40Percent amount = 0.4 * self.Member__Annual_Earnings__Salary elseif self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__BaseBuyUpPercentageforLTD = _50Percent amount = 0.5 * self.Member__Annual_Earnings__Salary elseif self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__BaseBuyUpPercentageforLTD = _60Percent amount = 0.6 * self.Member__Annual_Earnings__Salary else amount = 2 / 3 * self.Member__Annual_Earnings__Salary endIf endIf Result = amount endProc

procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFDate) var Coverage_Effective_Date : tWFDate var IncDay : Int4
;-----------Initial Enrollment Coverage Effective Date Calculation if self.Coverage__Enrollment_Period__Current_Enrollment_Period = cInitialEnrollment Coverage_Effective_Date = self.GBP__Effective_Date Result = Coverage_Effective_Date endIf ;----------Member Eligibility End Date for Ongoing Enrollment---------- if self.Coverage__Enrollment_Period__Current_Enrollment_Period = cOngoingEnrollment ;--------Increase the Number of Days by Waiting Period defined as Dynamic Data----- Coverage_Effective_Date = self.Contract__Signature_Date self.IncDays(self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodinDaysAfterEffectiveDate, Coverage_Effective_Date) ;--------Coverage Effective Date is First of the Month) if self.DateAsDay(Coverage_Effective_Date) = 1 Result = Coverage_Effective_Date else self.IncMonths(1, Coverage_Effective_Date) self.SetDay(1, Coverage_Effective_Date) Result = Coverage_Effective_Date endIf endIf endProc

if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(1, 5, 'Coverage__Dynamic_Data__AdditionalBenefitforLTD') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFPercent) var base : Decimal var total : Decimal
if self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__BaseBuyUpPercentageforLTD = _40Percent base = 0.4 elseif self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__BaseBuyUpPercentageforLTD = _50Percent base = 0.5 elseif self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__BaseBuyUpPercentageforLTD = _60Percent base = 0.6 else base = 2 / 3 endIf total = Decimal(self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__AdditionalBenefitforLTD) + base ;Member Contribution if self.Coverage__Classifications__LTDBenefitPlan = BaseBuyUp Result = 0 else Result = Decimal(self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__AdditionalBenefitforLTD) / total endIf endProc

aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLI_LifeDisabilityRuleEngine) (Def Version:2) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFTypes, aWLIMemberContractRoot

procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Boolean) var Eligibility_End_Date : tWFDate
Result = False ;------------Member Eligibility End Date Calculation--------------- Eligibility_End_Date = self.Member__HireDate + self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WaitingPeriodinDaysAfterEffectiveDate ;-----------Late Entrant Underwriting Rule------------- if self.Coverage__Enrollment_Period__Current_Enrollment_Period = cOngoingEnrollment if self.Contract__Signature_Date > Eligibility_End_Date + self.Coverage__Grace_Period_Nb_Days Result = True self.AppendComment('This Member enrollment is considered as late enrollment') endIf endIf if self.Insured__Age__At_Subscription > 50 Result = True self.AppendComment('Underwriting is required as the Insured age is greater than 50 years at subscription') endIf endProc
